4. Is there anything special we need to know in order to run your code?

There was an error with the assessibility saying that the color contrast between the text and the background were not valid.
However, when checked with a contrast checker, the two colors used were valid.
Included in the validity check screenshots is a screenshot of the contrast checker called valid-colorContrast.png